commentary: Carter to Mathews, 1 leg bye that could be tight but was Mathews sent back just in time? Full length delivery, the ball sneaks past Mathews' defence and hits him on the thigh before rolling back along the pitch, Mathews runs thinking there is a single but he is sent back just in time. Carter does exceptionally well to run in and kick the ball onto the stumps with his foot but Angelo's diving effort saves him. They get an extra also
